			"content_html": "<p>“One of our two major parties appears to be hopelessly, irredeemably corrupt. And unless that party not only loses this year’s election but begins losing on a regular basis, America as we know it is finished.” —<a href=\"https://nyti.ms/2l4R3GM?smid=nytcore-ios-share\">Paul Krugman</a></p>\n",
